<Author>jojomillar
<Content>Love Sitges...Loved The Melia.... This is our second trip to Sitges.We booked direct with hotel and booked a standard room for 拢 65 (room only) .We asked for a sea view and high floor ( there are only 6 floors). We flew to Barcelona and got the train ( Change at El Prat 2.50 euros ...bargain) There are taxis at the station to take you to the hotel.The check in was good and they had our request and we got a lovely room. Decor was good nice balcony, lovely view... Mini bar, hairdryer etc. There is room service if you want it. We joined the MAS card scheme online so you can get a 2 for 1 breakfast ,which we did a couple of days. I was really impressed ,the fruit was to die for and Champers if you fancy an early morning tipple !!!The MAS card also gets you a late checkout at no additional cost which was handy. The pool area is lovely..comfy beds and towels provided....the pool itself was great . It was quiet but that suited us .Good restaurant service by the pool the....choice and quality was good. Sitges is 15min walk from the hotel you can't get lost...there is a scenic walk which takes slightly longer but the views are great.You can also get taxi, Sitges is great lots of windy cobbled streets ....good shopping and fab restaurants and bars. The night life can get interesting...anythings goes...it's great to have a cava and watch the world go by. There was a festival on when we were there which was good fun.We discovered the Marina this time..... it's only 5mins walk from the hotel.....be warned the steps are steep.....you can go other ways which is easier on the legs. The Marina was bustling at the weekend...lots of restaurants and a few cocktail bars...a nice way to spend an evening.We headed up to Barcelona for the day took about 40mins... 5 Euro return the train takes you right to the the Centre. Barcelona is a lovely city something for everyone, well worth a visit.Will definitely return to Sitges and would highly recommend the Melia. The Staff were very professional and courteous....Thanks for a nice stay !!! I want to go back !!! 
